Drinks were reasonable, the karaoke DJ was great and has a helluva voice, and the atmosphere was fun. Not sure what was with the donuts but they looked and smelled amazing! Looking for some fun on a Friday night? Go check out Zazou’s and some karaoke.

I wandered in on an 87° afternoon after work and encountered IMMEDIATE service, an ICY COLD beer! I was informed that it was happy hour with drink specials and half price appetizers. I finished beer #1 in no time,ordered another and asked about the food specials. I decided on the pretzel sticks with queso. They came a short time later and I thought I'd died and gone to heaven!!! I've NEVER experienced pretzels like these! Buttery,crispy,salty and like cotton candy in lightness and mouth feel ! Service was attentive without being overbearing.  It was an overall fantastic experience out of nowhere!!!
